<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><aka>Hatak hʋsh puta ma!, Ile-kostinechi.</aka>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Hatak hʋsh puta ma!
.    
     Oh 'le kostinechi,
 Hʋsh yamoho̱mi pulla cha,
.    
     Hʋchi okcha̱yashke.

[V2]
 Kʋna fehna hocha,
.    
     I̱ nan ashʋchi ya̱.
 Isht anukha̱klo keyu kʋt
.    
     Ik i̱ kashofoshke.

[V3]
 Amba nukha̱klok mʋt,
.    
     Chisʋs i̱ yushobʋt,
 Okpulot kʋniat a̱ya,
.    
     Tuk kia, yokpashke.

[V4]
 Mikma Chihowa hʋt,
.    
     Nan ashʋchi keyu,
 Makinli ho̱ chohmichi hosh,
.    
     Holitobli hoke.</lyrics>
<title>Repentance. ƲIT167</title>
<time_sig>S.M. (6.6.8.6.)</time_sig>
<hymn_number>167</hymn_number>
</song>